name: AVS 1*
avsText: Find shots of one or more people eating food at a table indoors

name: KIS Textual 12
text1: A dark skinned man with a gray hat standind under a curved roof and talks into a microphone. His name is displayed at the beginning.
text2: A dark skinned man with a gray hat standind under a curved roof and talks into a microphone. His name is displayed at the beginning, in a yellow box. He is called Dojival Vieira and wears a black shirt.
text3: A dark skinned man with a gray hat standind under a curved roof and talks into a microphone. His name is displayed at the beginning, in a yellow box. He is called Dojival Viera and wears a black shirt. The roof is white. Houses and trees are visible behind the man on the left.

name: AVS 12*
avsText: Find shots of at least two planes both visible

name: KIS Textual 4
text1: An Asian woman in a hardware store testing red paint on the wall. Male shop assistant cuts a wooden board. The women opens many exhibited doors.
text2: An Asian woman in a hardware store testing red paint on the wall. Male shop assistant cuts a wooden board. The women opens many exhibited doors. Video is slightly fast forward, and has orange text overlay at the top and then left.
text3: An Asian woman in a hardware store testing red paint on the wall. Male shop assistant cuts a wooden board. The women opens many exhibited doors. Video is slightly fast forward, and has orange text overlay at the top and then left. Woman carries a large orange bag, with white writing "B&Q".

name: AVS 21*
avsText: Find shots of a person riding a horse including horse-drawn carts

name: KIS Textual 13
text1: A bearded man with glasses in a storehouse. He walks between boxes to the right and puts something on a shelf.
text2: A bearded man with glasses in a storehouse. He walks between boxes to the right and puts something on a shelf. The camera follows the man closely, showing only head and shoulders.
text3: A bearded man with glasses in a storehouse. He walks between boxes to the right and puts something on a shelf. The camera follows the man closely, showing only head and shoulders. He has dark hair and wears a orange/brownish pullover. There shelfs have yellow and red supports.

name: AVS 9*
avsText: Find shots of an adult person running in a city street

name: KIS Textual 14
text1: A man with a black jacket and glasses sitting at a desk, a secretary standing left of him, handing him papers to sign.
text2: A man with a black jacket and glasses sitting at a desk, a secretary standing left of him, handing him papers to sign. A wooden door is on the left in the background, a phone is on the right side of the desk.
text3: A calendar with months forming a white/gray checkerboard is on the wall behind the desk.
